{"tid":749233,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有版規，永遠冇真相。有實名，冇真相。自由冇版規，都冇真相。互聯網只有分化，冇真相。","createTime":"2018-07-20T01:08:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T10:44:44.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c69f2a6542b293ab7c10938926f8f4446cfb3106","tid":749233,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:08:49.000Z","msg":"香討，高登，連登都係香港熱門討論區<br />\n<br />\n香討有版規，只要同版主立場唔同，都有機會被人用藉口刪post甚至禁言（如人身攻擊，惡意批評等）。相反，同版主同一立場，即使真有人身攻擊，post照keep。<br />\n<br />\n例子係香港時事政治台。版主親共，所以大量親共五毛post。即使係人身攻擊有理無理喪屌黃絲，post都健在。<br />\n<br />\n相反，黃絲屌五毛，就會好快被刪除，叫惡意評論，被扣分。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好啦，久而久之，即使香討唔多存在收錢五毛，都會變親共人士的天堂。因為版主不停ko黃絲的post，只歡迎親共者。<br />\n<br />\n（香討係咪有真大量收政府錢五毛？唔知。不過同一樣，被人任改的wikipedia網站，著名程度遠高於香討，都一樣有好多反共條目。所以香討問題，似乎係版主因素最多。）<br />\n<br />\n好啦，頂唔順香討班友，就走過去第二些討論區。高登仔、連登仔好多都係頂唔順香討版主管理走過黎。<br />\n<br />\n頂唔順香討的，多數係黃絲多，又學埋香港五毛野，只係立場唔同。所以高登和連登，好多屈毛黨。只要一親共，就聯手反對。<br />\n<br />\n咁自由化的高登和連登可否代表香港，當然係唔得。因為都係聚集頂唔順香討管理班人。所以連登只能代表，反對香討版主管理的一班人的聲音，唔能夠代表整個香港。<br />\n<br />\n為左避免有marketer和真五毛來影響討論區的立場和氣氛。高登、連登只限isp和校園email。但咁樣，會否代表我們距離真相近一些。當然唔可以啦。因為大部分人都唔識register and use ISP電郵，所以好快會變成以 IT 狗的討論區。而因為校園email都得，所以多年輕人。而高登、連登只係一班學生和IT狗為方主，喂喂喂的討論區。唔可以代表到香港整體立場。<br />\n<br />\n所以，因為各大網站的版規，限制。<br />\n在互聯網上，只有立場分化，沒有真相的存在。"},{"pid":"86378f1c543bcb70efd2930554b10aeafa8ccb09","tid":749233,"uid":51021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:15:13.000Z","msg":"joe哥沉左幾日又發功？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856227e8e4218bb4369d8381bea6a532f8211694","tid":749233,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"86378f1c543bcb70efd2930554b10aeafa8ccb09","tid":749233,"uid":51021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:15:13.000Z","msg":"joe哥沉左幾日又發功？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:18:37.000Z","msg":"講下你點睇"},{"pid":"83ef10ab1f28b5fb485d3d099bebf5e27afc89a0","tid":749233,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/115947_7f5aa2cf442a0921ac98ad02b8764719.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F115947_7f5aa2cf442a0921ac98ad02b8764719.png&h=4bc2b1c3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/115948_e9d0dd0a3d85ac107a6d00fac57413a8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F115948_e9d0dd0a3d85ac107a6d00fac57413a8.png&h=8d833962&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/115949_e9d0dd0a3d85ac107a6d00fac57413a8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F115949_e9d0dd0a3d85ac107a6d00fac57413a8.png&h=6594a9c3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/115949_31d6ab1a5728ca927c97c09e3c77ea95.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F115949_31d6ab1a5728ca927c97c09e3c77ea95.png&h=d9e8f974&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/115950_31d6ab1a5728ca927c97c09e3c77ea95.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F115950_31d6ab1a5728ca927c97c09e3c77ea95.png&h=bdbe7137&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6751e503f366adf71b08be5d1c248204a1bff1f6","tid":749233,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83ef10ab1f28b5fb485d3d099bebf5e27afc89a0","tid":749233,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/115947_7f5aa2cf442a0921ac98ad02b8764719.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F115947_7f5aa2cf442a0921ac98ad02b8764719.png&h=4bc2b1c3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/115948_e9d0dd0a3d85ac107a6d00fac57413a8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F115948_e9d0dd0a3d85ac107a6d00fac57413a8.png&h=8d833962&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/115949_e9d0dd0a3d85ac107a6d00fac57413a8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F115949_e9d0dd0a3d85ac107a6d00fac57413a8.png&h=6594a9c3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/115949_31d6ab1a5728ca927c97c09e3c77ea95.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F115949_31d6ab1a5728ca927c97c09e3c77ea95.png&h=d9e8f974&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/115950_31d6ab1a5728ca927c97c09e3c77ea95.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F115950_31d6ab1a5728ca927c97c09e3c77ea95.png&h=bdbe7137&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T10:40:19.000Z","msg":"現家就係想知真正（冇左五毛，討論區又易登記下）香港人對政治的立場。"},{"pid":"03e7a39b631d6df014c8c84e608e8c6bd6b034c9","tid":749233,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T10:44:44.000Z","msg":"好多2004年後上網的，特別智能手機普及先上網的，都只識web based email ，甚至只識用gmail, yahoo mail，唔識set up pop3 email，而多數isp又用pop3 email，冇web based email。<br />\n<br />\n而且好多人係，一個大約4個人家庭，共用一個isp account。<br />\n<br />\n所以isp email係very user unfriendly<br />\n<br />\nSms就人人都識，每個人都有1部電話，所以好好多。<br />\n<br />\nsample 冇isp email咁biased。"}]}